text: João Jens was a volleyball player from Brazil. João competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. He was born on 3 June 1944 and died on 10 December 2020.João Jens == References == Category:1944 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Brazilian volleyball players Category:Olympians for Brazil Category:Sportspeople from São Paulo
